  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 3 \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1 -\u00a0 3 \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd, 05 \u0ba4\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 bicycle thieves arrested in Manthi East - 3 bicycles, 05 water pumps recovered!",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three suspects have been arrested and 3 bicycles and 05 water pumps have been recovered in connection with the bicycle theft incidents that have been happening for a long time in Mullaitivu Manthi East.",
        "A person who was involved in theft of bicycles and theft of water pumps and selling them in several areas under the Mullaitivu Natangandal police division was caught by the public and handed over to the police after stealing a bicycle from a grocery store.",
        "Subsequently, a team led by the Officer-in-Charge of Natangandal Police Station was involved in the investigation and with the cooperation of the public, the arrest was made.",
        ".A person involved in theft of bicycles has been identified and two more persons associated with him from Manthi East have been arrested and 03 bicycles and 05 water pumps have been recovered from them.",
        "In this case, the Natangandal police have said that they have taken steps to present them in Mullaitivu District Magistrate Court today 05.07.2022."
      ],
